# Configuration Files

This project generates and manages several configuration files:

## ESLint Configuration
- [index.cjs](mdc:index.cjs) - The main ESLint configuration exported by the package
- [template/config/.eslintrc.cjs](mdc:template/config/.eslintrc.cjs) - Template for user's ESLint config
- [template/config/.eslintignore](mdc:template/config/.eslintignore) - Template for ESLint ignore patterns

## Prettier Configuration
- [template/config/.prettierrc](mdc:template/config/.prettierrc) - Template for Prettier configuration
- [template/config/.prettierignore](mdc:template/config/.prettierignore) - Template for Prettier ignore patterns

## Installation Methods
1. **Standard Install**: Use the package as an ESLint extension (`extends: ['ts-prefixer']`)
2. **Barebone Install**: Copy the configuration files directly to your project for customization

All configurations focus on meaningful lint rules for runtime behavior and consistent formatting with Prettier integration.
